+### Refresh Token
+- **Storage**: HTTP-only secure cookies (server-controlled)
+- **Lifetime**: Long-lived (7-30 days)
+- **Usage**: Automatic token refresh
+- **Security**: Client-side á€™á€¾ access á€™á€›
